---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — MandarinPath"
  description="Privacy policy for MandarinPath, an AI-powered Chinese language learning app."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-20">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-mandarin-700">Last updated: July 3, 2026</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-700">
      MandarinPath is built to help learners practice Chinese with personalized feedback.
      This policy explains the basic information we collect, how we use it, and how to
      contact us with questions.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-slate-700">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          We may collect account details such as your email address, learning preferences,
          progress data, and practice submissions. For speaking practice, this can include
          audio recordings you choose to submit for pronunciation feedback.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">How We Use Information</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          We use this information to provide the MandarinPath service, personalize your
          learning experience, evaluate practice tasks, improve product quality, prevent
          abuse, and respond to support requests.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Service Providers</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          We may use trusted service providers for hosting, authentication, analytics,
          speech evaluation, and other product functions. These providers process
          information only as needed to support MandarinPath.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Your Choices</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          You can contact us to request access, correction, or deletion of your account
          information. Some information may be retained when required for security,
          legal compliance, or service integrity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          For privacy questions, contact
          <a class="font-medium text-mandarin-700 hover:text-mandarin-800" href="mailto:support@mandarinpath.com">
            support@mandarinpath.com</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
